                     <incipit><q xml:lang="gez"><choice>
                              <sic>ሜኒ፡</sic>
                              <corr>ዘያሜኒ፡</corr>
                           </choice> ኵሎ፡ ወዘያስተሴፉ፡ ጥዑመ፡ ዜና፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ለኃሊብ፡ <choice>
                              <sic>ዕጐል፡</sic>
                              <corr>ዕጐልት፡</corr>
                           </choice> ሱታፉ፡ <sic>ሰምከ፡</sic>
